_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/ff88449926c54d4439fef624ded6f567.avif?t=1759346697\" width=599 height=171 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An untroubled routine of serene daily life gets destroyed in one brief moment - a devastating fire leaves your girlfriend in a coma. You’re heartbroken, lost, and left with so many questions unanswered that you start wondering about how and why, and little clues here and there raise even more questions whatsoever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/140934f402750de1cb60d1a3dfcb1085.poster.avif?t=1759346697\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/140934f402750de1cb60d1a3dfcb1085.webm?t=1759346697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/140934f402750de1cb60d1a3dfcb1085.mp4?t=1759346697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A secret hidden behind all of this pulls you into one hell of a journey as you’re tasked with rebuilding your relationship from scratch - after the coma she seems to have a severe amnesia case. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/07ecbe77f62e848c6591422239ae7f63.avif?t=1759346697\" width=599 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From first dates to intimate moments, every step reveals more about her past and the mysteries surrounding the tragedy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172280/extras/8f56f501504882f78920e7accd47bc6f.poster.avif?t=1759346697\" width=600 height=388 